animals.description: Nutritional specifications for Ross 308 broilers based on different target live weights.

crude_protein.notes: Formulation should focus on achieving an adequate amino acid profile. Crude protein level is not a requirement per se but instead a level likely achievable in corn/wheat and soybean meal-based diets to ensure a functional pool of non-essential amino acids [16].

stages.key_notes: Feed specifications should be used as a guide only; adjustments may be necessary for local conditions, legislation and markets [14]. A withdrawal feed should be fed to meet local requirements for medication withdrawal times and can be formulated to the same standards as the final feed listed [14].
